{"tid":1083573,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人女朋友嘅家姐或細妹正過自己女朋友好多？","createTime":"2019-03-29T17:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T17:34:30.000Z","uid":104017,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ffba564cd409f0101c2ead981987725cefed3ea","tid":1083573,"uid":104017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:00:14.000Z","msg":"女朋友唔係差<br />\n有170高 唔太白<br />\n普通樣但有靚腳<br />\n可惜得細B<br />\n一隻手就揸得哂兩邊波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（可能我手大）<br />\n佢有一個大一年嘅家姐<br />\n好！撚！正！<br />\n樣靚都不在話下<br />\n仲又瘦又白又滑<br />\n起碼有172高<br />\n最重要係心口好大包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n偷睇過佢D bra<br />\n原來有D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次見到佢著吊帶<br />\n都扯到硬一硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後忍唔住拉條女入房執返兩劑<br />\n幻想屌緊佢家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時喺度諗<br />\n點解唔係識佢家姐先呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89769493519648c660e7ff43495ed85143b26de7","tid":1083573,"uid":119627,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"至少人哋男友/老公好你好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbc3e0162bd134f1e520e2d691cddbd5109408b","tid":1083573,"uid":104017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89769493519648c660e7ff43495ed85143b26de7","tid":1083573,"uid":119627,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"至少人哋男友/老公好你好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"佢單身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />身"},{"pid":"a0153180e8e81efa44990a5035a6d20ec3575b3d","tid